That's great!

295
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:06,880
All our hard work pays off.

296
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:07,390
Erduo.

297
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:09,090
You're not in the right mood.

298
00:18:09,610 --> 00:18:10,370
Get more excited.

299
00:18:18,660 --> 00:18:19,380
Really?

300
00:18:20,140 --> 00:18:20,850
That's great.

301
00:18:21,280 --> 00:18:22,010
All our hard work pays...

302
00:18:22,010 --> 00:18:22,290
Stop.

303
00:18:23,180 --> 00:18:24,470
Why are you getting more depressed?

304
00:18:25,410 --> 00:18:25,930
Do it again.

305
00:18:28,770 --> 00:18:29,520
Really?

306
00:18:30,030 --> 00:18:30,960
That's great.

307
00:18:31,260 --> 00:18:33,800
All our hard work pays...

308
00:18:34,360 --> 00:18:35,890
Are you riding a roller coaster?

309
00:18:36,140 --> 00:18:37,220
You're getting lower and lower.

310
00:18:38,220 --> 00:18:39,660
Sorry, Mr. Xu, sorry.

311
00:18:39,840 --> 00:18:41,330
I'll do it again.

312
00:18:41,330 --> 00:18:42,140
I'm sorry.

313
00:18:43,110 --> 00:18:44,060
That's it for today.

314
00:18:51,040 --> 00:18:52,080
What's wrong with you today?

315
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:53,760
Do you still want to be a voice actress
or not?

316
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:57,100
I'm sorry, Mr. Xu.

317
00:18:57,620 --> 00:18:58,780
I don't care what happened to you.

318
00:18:59,690 --> 00:19:00,470
When you're in the recording studio,

319
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:02,080
you have to get rid of the other things

320
00:19:02,080 --> 00:19:02,660
on your mind.

321
00:19:03,560 --> 00:19:04,820
You're working here, you know?

322
00:19:05,940 --> 00:19:07,690
Don't bring other emotions into the work.

323
00:19:08,220 --> 00:19:09,700
This is also against the work ethics

324
00:19:09,700 --> 00:19:10,650
of a professional voice actress.

325
00:19:13,590 --> 00:19:15,070
I got it, Mr. Xu.

326
00:19:15,220 --> 00:19:16,440
I will pay attention next time.

327
00:19:19,010 --> 00:19:19,360
OK.

328
00:19:20,630 --> 00:19:21,310
You can go back.

329
00:19:22,510 --> 00:19:23,850
Organize your emotions.

330
00:19:43,250 --> 00:19:44,590
Erduo, have some water.

331
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:47,010
Mr. Xu is always a strict person.

332
00:19:47,510 --> 00:19:49,010
Don't take it personally.

333
