She should.

334
00:19:52,890 --> 00:19:54,290
Or she could not make progress.

335
00:19:54,490 --> 00:19:55,220
Stop it.

336
00:19:56,370 --> 00:19:59,070
Something is bothering her.

337
00:20:00,080 --> 00:20:01,770
Don't you want to be a professional?

338
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:03,100
Would a professional

339
00:20:03,100 --> 00:20:04,770
ever make such a silly mistake?

340
00:20:05,380 --> 00:20:06,770
You were wasting your time

341
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,420
and ours, too.

342
00:20:09,100 --> 00:20:10,420
Shouldn't she get a reprimand?

343
00:20:17,270 --> 00:20:18,260
I'm sorry.

344
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:22,740
I wasted your precious time today.

345
00:20:24,720 --> 00:20:25,310
It's OK.

346
00:20:25,860 --> 00:20:27,480
We all have bad moods sometimes.

347
00:20:28,120 --> 00:20:29,330
We should understand each other.

348
00:20:30,150 --> 00:20:31,280
Let's go home now.

349
00:21:17,180 --> 00:21:18,280
Bei Erduo, you're still here?

350
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:20,250
Why are you crying so sadly?

351
00:21:22,070 --> 00:21:26,330
I... I'm reading lines of the next scene.

352
00:21:28,170 --> 00:21:29,540
Then we will leave you to it.

353
00:21:29,540 --> 00:21:30,170
Take your time.

354
00:22:19,980 --> 00:22:20,490
Li,

355
00:22:22,260 --> 00:22:23,400
