356
00:22:24,370 --> 00:22:25,600
Give this to Boss Yu later.

357
00:22:25,710 --> 00:22:26,750
[Employee's Card]

358
00:22:26,780 --> 00:22:28,630
Um, where are you going?

359
00:22:31,060 --> 00:22:31,790
I'm taking a long vacation.

360
00:22:32,250 --> 00:22:33,070
Work hard.

361
00:22:36,190 --> 00:22:36,900
Hi, Ms. Tang.

362
00:22:37,330 --> 00:22:37,840
Hi.

363
00:22:42,990 --> 00:22:50,630
[LOVING]

364
00:23:23,700 --> 00:23:24,220
Ms. Tang.

365
00:23:29,190 --> 00:23:35,710
[SUGARENT ENTERTAINMENT]

366
00:23:45,610 --> 00:23:48,770
Master, here's your special magic coffee.

367
00:23:49,680 --> 00:23:51,720
The magic has begun.

368
00:23:56,100 --> 00:23:57,760
It's beautiful. Thank you.

369
00:24:04,120 --> 00:24:06,760
What can I do for you, Master?

370
00:24:07,690 --> 00:24:08,820
Magic Americano, please.

371
00:24:38,290 --> 00:24:41,930
Master, you've been reading this book
for two days.

372
00:24:42,130 --> 00:24:43,790
Shall I get another one for you?

373
00:24:45,810 --> 00:24:47,300
Maybe I don't remember its content.

374
00:24:47,450 --> 00:24:48,640
I just want to read it again.

375
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:49,370
Right?

376
00:24:51,550 --> 00:24:53,420
If you're idle,

377
00:24:55,140 --> 00:24:56,160
you can read this one.

378
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:57,720
It helps you learn the Japanese language.

379
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:01,460
I'm here to relax.

380
00:25:13,760 --> 00:25:15,380
This is your reward. Drink it.

381
00:25:15,380 --> 00:25:16,050
Your... Your hands.

382
00:25:16,050 --> 00:25:16,720
Erduo.

383
00:25:17,430 --> 00:25:18,080
Yes.

384
00:25:21,430 --> 00:25:25,070
[Dewei Tower]

385
00:26:04,540 --> 00:26:08,440
The number you dialed is busy,
please try again later.

386
00:26:14,790 --> 00:26:16,230
[Ye Shuwei]

387
00:26:16,230 --> 00:26:18,710
[Bus 25]

388
00:26:53,730 --> 00:26:55,670
I didn't swindle you out of your money.

389
00:26:56,320 --> 00:26:57,470
Our money...

390
00:26:58,280 --> 00:27:01,250
Our money is gone forever.

391
00:27:05,420 --> 00:27:06,990
Are you riding a roller coaster?

392
00:27:07,360 --> 00:27:08,590
You're getting lower and lower.

393
00:27:09,480 --> 00:27:10,960
Sorry, Mr. Xu, sorry.

394
00:28:26,040 --> 00:28:26,960
OK, thanks.

395
00:28:35,760 --> 00:28:37,910
Now please allow me to convey

396
00:28:37,910 --> 00:28:40,310
my best wishes for your love.

397
00:29:16,930 --> 00:29:17,520
Thank you.

398
00:29:17,860 --> 00:29:18,420
Thank you.

399
00:29:18,890 --> 00:29:19,920
That was a great dance.

400
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:20,830
Yes.

401
00:29:30,320 --> 00:29:31,430
Why are you here again?

402
00:29:31,610 --> 00:29:33,400
I've been here for so many times.

403
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:34,750
You've never danced for me.

404
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:39,930
They ordered the lovers' package.

405
00:29:39,930 --> 00:29:41,090
A single man can't order it.

406
00:29:41,620 --> 00:29:42,900
I'm not single.

407
00:29:43,410 --> 00:29:44,560
I have you.

408
00:29:44,950 --> 00:29:45,710
Stop it.

409
00:29:47,740 --> 00:29:49,320
What would you like to order, Master?

410
00:29:50,820 --> 00:29:53,170
I'll have a cappuccino and a blueberry cake.

411
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:55,490
Wait a minute.

412
00:29:56,230 --> 00:29:58,290
Remember to apply this balm
to the burn every day.

413
00:30:00,100 --> 00:30:00,620
Thank you.

414
00:30:06,500 --> 00:30:08,510
Xin, I want to put this here first.

415
00:30:08,510 --> 00:30:09,660
I'll take it home when I leave.

416
00:30:09,660 --> 00:30:10,110
OK.

417
00:30:10,370 --> 00:30:11,210
Welcome.

418
00:30:15,380 --> 00:30:16,840
He's here again. Your boyfriend?

419
00:30:17,780 --> 00:30:19,560
Don't make fun of me, Xin.

420
00:30:19,560 --> 00:30:21,110
So he likes you?

421
00:30:22,040 --> 00:30:23,640
Xin, enough with your wild guess.

422
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:25,120
He's just one of my students,

423
00:30:25,120 --> 00:30:26,330
like a younger brother to me.

424
00:30:28,230 --> 00:30:28,840
Is it done?

425
00:30:28,840 --> 00:30:29,970
Yes, take it.

426
00:30:39,530 --> 00:30:40,110
Please enjoy it.

427
00:30:40,110 --> 00:30:40,750
Wait a minute.

428
00:30:42,020 --> 00:30:43,770
Having ordered

429
00:30:43,770 --> 00:30:45,480
all 10 packages on your menu,

430
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:46,810
I finally gathered all 10 maid cards.

431
00:30:47,240 --> 00:30:49,390
As a rule, you have to play a game with me.

432
00:30:50,350 --> 00:30:52,240
I want you to dance for me.

433
00:30:54,370 --> 00:30:56,020
That's for the lovers' package.

434
00:30:56,630 --> 00:30:57,820
Well,

435
00:31:00,770 --> 00:31:03,600
I want you to do the Sailor Moon dance.

436
00:31:08,900 --> 00:31:11,360
If only you can win the game.

437
00:31:12,410 --> 00:31:12,920
Which do you want to play?

438
00:31:16,600 --> 00:31:17,090
That.

439
00:31:18,020 --> 00:31:21,620
Jump, jump, jump.

440
00:31:21,620 --> 00:31:25,410
Jump, jump, jump.

441
00:31:26,740 --> 00:31:27,520
Your turn.

442
00:31:28,080 --> 00:31:28,860
Jump.

443
00:31:28,860 --> 00:31:29,490
Jump.

444
00:31:30,270 --> 00:31:30,930
OK.

445
00:31:30,930 --> 00:31:31,550
Jump.

446
00:31:31,550 --> 00:31:32,900
Jump.

447
00:31:32,970 --> 00:31:34,000
Jump.

448
00:31:39,870 --> 00:31:41,010
Do you really want it?

449
00:31:49,600 --> 00:31:51,120
I'm Sailor Moon.

450
00:31:51,620 --> 00:31:54,140
On behalf of the moon, I will destroy you.

451
00:32:31,680 --> 00:32:32,370
Do you need help?

452
00:32:32,740 --> 00:32:33,380
No, she doesn't.

453
00:32:48,670 --> 00:32:49,670
Do you want this book?

454
00:32:50,860 --> 00:32:51,570
Thank you very much.

455
00:33:02,660 --> 00:33:04,110
How long have you been standing behind me?

456
00:33:04,570 --> 00:33:05,090
Five minutes.

457
00:33:06,770 --> 00:33:07,840
Five minutes?

458
00:33:08,980 --> 00:33:11,060
You just watched me stand on my tiptoes

459
00:33:11,060 --> 00:33:12,450
and failed to reach it.

460
00:33:18,370 --> 00:33:20,790
Can you spare some goodwill for others?

461
00:33:21,150 --> 00:33:22,900
You never looked back to ask for help.

462
00:33:47,910 --> 00:33:48,330
Hello?

463
00:33:48,870 --> 00:33:49,360
Boss.

464
00:33:50,040 --> 00:33:51,760
Some changes in the violin order

465
00:33:51,760 --> 00:33:52,480
for Emily's Orchestra.

466
00:33:53,060 --> 00:33:54,300
The person in charge

467
00:33:54,300 --> 00:33:56,280
wishes to talk face to face soon.

468
00:33:56,870 --> 00:33:58,210
I just called them.

469
00:33:59,950 --> 00:34:01,200
They want to know if it's convenient
for you today.

470
00:34:01,200 --> 00:34:02,200
[Japanese ABC New Edition]

471
00:34:04,900 --> 00:34:05,780
Does it have to be today?

472
00:34:06,650 --> 00:34:08,000
They didn't say.

473
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:10,220
If it's not convenient for you,

474
00:34:11,200 --> 00:34:13,200
I can call back and put it off.

475
00:34:13,970 --> 00:34:15,170
Try to schedule it for two days later.

476
00:34:23,890 --> 00:34:24,670
Have you made a choice yet?

477
00:34:31,640 --> 00:34:34,000
[An Actor Prepares]

478
00:34:57,140 --> 00:34:57,850
Here's your receipt.

479
00:35:05,170 --> 00:35:05,690
Hello.

480
00:35:05,910 --> 00:35:07,840
Sorry, I don't want this book.

481
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:08,980
It's OK, just give it to me.

482
00:35:16,670 --> 00:35:17,160
Together.

483
00:35:21,890 --> 00:35:22,370
Thank you.

484
00:35:34,610 --> 00:35:35,200
What's wrong with you?

485
00:35:35,730 --> 00:35:37,110
Is something bothering you?

486
00:35:39,370 --> 00:35:40,970
If it's because of me, I can apologize.

487
00:35:44,460 --> 00:35:45,220
I'm OK.

488
00:36:14,030 --> 00:36:14,550
Er...

489
00:36:40,600 --> 00:36:41,920
