492
00:37:45,890 --> 00:37:46,370
Just in time.

493
00:37:52,840 --> 00:37:53,980
Thank you very much.

494
00:37:59,600 --> 00:38:00,430
Go home and sleep early.

495
00:38:02,080 --> 00:38:03,140
Look at your eyes.

496
00:38:04,430 --> 00:38:05,720
