497
00:38:11,540 --> 00:38:13,790
It's the result of my immortal cultivation.

498
00:38:14,450 --> 00:38:15,770
Few people have it.

499
00:38:15,970 --> 00:38:16,990
Including you.

500
00:38:21,050 --> 00:38:22,670
I should go home and sleep.

501
00:38:23,490 --> 00:38:24,900
Drive safe.

502
00:38:36,080 --> 00:38:36,580
Wait a minute.

503
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:57,360
I bought these books for you.

504
00:39:03,450 --> 00:39:04,570
[Basic Dubbing Practice]
[Contextual Practice]

