00:39:09,340 --> 00:39:10,260
Thank you very much.

506
00:39:14,220 --> 00:39:15,210
I'll leave now.

507
00:39:15,860 --> 00:39:16,290
Good night.

508
00:39:17,790 --> 00:39:18,300
Good night.

